{
  "name": "魯芭的靈魂塔羅卡 Luba『s Tarokka of Souls",
  "type": "equipment",
  "img": "icons/sundries/misc/admission-ticket-grey.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">並非所有逗留於</span><span class=\"GramE\">世</span>的靈魂都是迷失在通往死後國度之路上的悲慘靈魂。有些靈魂失去活力，成爲了囚徒；它們是如此邪惡，以至於凡人不敢將它們釋放到那毫無戒心的來世。<br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">作為由維斯塔尼傳說中的人物創造的物品，</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>魯</em></span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>芭</em></span><em>的</em><span class=\"GramE\"><em>靈魂塔羅卡</em></span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>|Luba</em></span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>『</em></span><em>s Tarokka of Souls</em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">塑造了無數英雄的命運。這套牌</span><span class=\"GramE\">作出</span>的預言也揭示了巨大的邪惡，引導它的創造者走入邪惡勢力的道路。牌組的創造者，魯芭夫人，依靠著她敏銳的直覺無數次僥倖逃離了自己的毀滅。但就算是她也無法躲過所有的邪惡。在最危急的關頭，魯芭夫人設法用命運的絲線封印住這些至惡的存在，將它們囚禁在了<span class=\"GramE\">這套塔羅卡中</span>。這些邪惡的靈魂被困於隱藏在卡<span class=\"GramE\">牌洗混翻轉</span>之中的地獄空間內，靜靜地等待著命運本身也被玷污的那一天——<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">這一天絕對會到來的。</span><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">和所有</span><span class=\"GramE\">塔羅卡組</span>一樣，<span class=\"GramE\">靈魂塔羅卡</span>是由五十四張插畫精美的卡片組成的，包含十四張至高牌以及四十張被分為錢幣，雕文，星星和寶劍<span class=\"GramE\">四個套組的</span>其他卡牌。<br /><em><strong>隨機屬性</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。這件神器具有以下隨機屬性，你可以通過對著<em>《地下城主指南》</em>中的</span>「<span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>神器</em></span> 」<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">章節擲</span><span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>以決定它們。</p><ul><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">兩項弱效增益屬性</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">兩項弱效減益屬性</span></li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><em><strong>法術</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。持握牌組時，你可以用一個動作用牌組施展以下法術（豁免</span>DC18<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">）：<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.v0KfpSysfp5ug9kx]{通曉語言Comprehend Languages}</em>，<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.zeN5fxXLn4QE2YDa]{偵測善惡Detect Evil and Good}</em>，<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.cGO3m3Xu4mtPegr4]{偵測魔法Detect Magic}</em>，</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.V3BKvj7g0q2XO0cg]{偵測毒素和疾病Detect Poison and DIsease}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">，</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.Fw3U8sQwWSPVoisW]{物品定位術Locate Object}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">，<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.OA4mCsVxg6nUrLjV]{探知Scrying}</em>。一旦你用牌組施展了某個法術，你在下一個黎明前不能再次施展該法術。</span><br /><em><strong>持久之視</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。持握牌組時，你為維持預言系法術的專注所作的體質豁免檢定自動成功。</span><br /><em><strong>編織命運</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。以一個動作，你可以從牌組中抽出一張卡，從而編織</span>15<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺內你能看見的另一個生物的命運。從以下效應中選擇一項：</span><br /><em><strong>幸福</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。在接下來的一小時內，該生物在攻擊檢定，屬性檢定和豁免檢定上具有優勢。</span><br /><em><strong>災禍</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。在接下來的一小時內，該生物在攻擊檢定，屬性檢定和豁免檢定上具有劣勢。</span><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">牌組可以如此被使用兩次，你在下一個黎明時分重</span><span class=\"GramE\">獲所有</span>已使用的次數。<br /><em><strong>命運的囚徒</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。每當你使用編織命運特性時，都有可能導致被囚禁的靈魂之一逃脫。</span><span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>一次[[/r 1d100]]<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">來</span><span class=\"GramE\">對照塔羅卡中</span>的靈魂表格。如果你<span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>出了至高牌之一，和它相關的靈魂就會逃脫。你可以在怪物圖鑑中找到它的數據。如果你<span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>出的靈魂已經逃脫了，則重<span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>。</p><table class=\"MsoTable15List1LightAccent1\" style=\"BORDER-COLLAPSE:collapse;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:-1;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;mso-yfti-lastfirstrow:yes\"><td style=\"BORDER-TOP:medium none;BORDER-RIGHT:medium none;BORDER-BOTTOM:#8eaadb 1pt solid;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;PADDING-TOP:0cm;PADDING-LEFT:5.4pt;BORDER-LEFT:medium none;PADDING-RIGHT:5.4pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid #8EAADB .5pt;mso-border-bottom-themecolor:accent1;mso-border-bottom-themetint:153\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN:center;mso-yfti-cnfc:5;text-align:center\"><strong>d100</strong></p></td><td style=\"BORDER-TOP:med